    "key": "output|Once_you_fully_commit_t_short_informs_you_that_it_s_station|1838dc18eeb7",
    "original": "Once you fully commit, \"+t.short+\" informs you that it’s station policy to ensure that inactivated ships have their storage completely emptied out. Ever since the entire deck got infested with grubthakks a few years back, it’s been something of a sore spot. <i>“Don’t worry too hard about it. Bolted-in upgrades are fine, and I’ll have your smaller things delivered to the new ship.”</i>",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "<<POS:10437709>>"
